ote14a\" data-full-marker=\"14а\">\n<p data-aid=\"121077975\" id=\"note14a_p1\"><small>АБО</small> олень, на якого полюють.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"19\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"а\" id=\"note19a\" data-full-marker=\"19а\">\n<p data-aid=\"121077976\" id=\"note19a_p1\"><small>ТОБТО</small> марнота.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"б\" id=\"note19b\" data-full-marker=\"19б\">\n<p data-aid=\"121077977\" id=\"note19b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/gen/19.24-25?lang=ukr#p24\">Бут. 19:24–25</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/deut/29.23?lang=ukr#p23\">Повтор. 29:23</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.9?lang=ukr#p9\">2 Неф. 13:9</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"20\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"а\" id=\"note20a\" data-full-marker=\"20а\">\n<p data-aid=\"121077978\" id=\"note20a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/jer/50.3,39-40?lang=ukr#p3\">Єр. 50:3, 39–40</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"21\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"а\" id=\"note21a\" data-full-marker=\"21а\">\n<p data-aid=\"121077979\" id=\"note21a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/34.14-15?lang=ukr#p14\">Ісая 34:14–15</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"б\" id=\"note21b\" data-full-marker=\"21б\">\n<p data-aid=\"121077980\" id=\"note21b_p1\"><small>ГЕБР</small> козли, або демони.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"22\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"а\" id=\"note22a\" data-full-marker=\"22а\">\n<p data-aid=\"121077981\" id=\"note22a_p1\"><small>ГЕБР</small> палацах.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"б\" id=\"note22b\" data-full-marker=\"22б\">\n<p data-aid=\"121077982\" id=\"note22b_p1\"><small>ГЕБР</small> (можливо) шакали або дикі собаки.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>